---
title: Sources
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /sources/
canonical: https://cheffist.com/sources/
---
<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-3xl border border-white/80 bg-white/90 p-8 shadow-panel">
  <p class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-frost px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-600">References</p>
  <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl">Sources Hub</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-slate-700">
    We prioritize public, reputable food safety references and apply them conservatively for household guidance.
    Sources are selected for authority, clarity, and applicability to storage behavior.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4">
    {% for source in sources %}
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-surface-900">
        <a class="hover:underline" href="{{ source.url }}">{{ source.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">{{ source.publisher }}</p>
      {% if source.notes %}
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">{{ source.notes }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if source.applies_to and source.applies_to.length > 0 %}
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate-500">
        Applies to: {{ source.applies_to | join(", ") }}
      </p>
      {% endif %}
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
